Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.88,0:02:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.24,0:02:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.42,0:02:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再那么说 绫音她给我化的妆会...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.07,0:02:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑沼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.40,0:02:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3秒 等我3秒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.62,0:02:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.15,0:03:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实 我对你的第一印象就很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.34,0:03:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是对我微笑了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.17,0:03:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在入学典礼之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.16,0:03:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为我指路的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.39,0:03:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们进了同一个班
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.39,0:03:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我再也没见过像那时候的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.39,0:03:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直很在意 你是什么样的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.12,0:21:04.42,Warning,NTP,0000,0000,0000,banner;28;0;60,翻译 瑶瑶 老虎 时间 校译 阿虚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.28,0:03:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原本以为
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.99,0:03:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他早忘了我们一次见面的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.78,0:03:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你一定是个好人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.56,0:03:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其实比我想像中还要好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.48,0:03:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要好?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.76,0:03:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以认为他觉得“我不错”吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.77,0:03:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天又变化这么大 让我大吃一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.64,0:04:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 没想到吓到您了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.75,0:04:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 不是的 不是那个意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.81,0:04:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.23,0:04:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是哪个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 别问了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.57,0:04:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去排队参拜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.52,0:04:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就是新年了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.06,0:04:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改变了哦 变好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.76,0:04:34.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说我改变了 也许真的是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你见到胡桃的时候不是想过要变得可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.75,0:04:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么想要变可爱 自己好好想想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.77,0:04:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫音 答案只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.11,0:04:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的变化让我的心情好纠结
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.01,0:05:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我想的要可爱太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.56,0:05:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前那个“想要成为风早同学那样的人”的我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.95,0:05:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在却希望“风早同学能觉得我有点可爱”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.64,0:05:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胳膊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.82,0:05:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么 要持续到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.54,0:05:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天知道 城对矢野她厌倦为止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.33,0:05:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 回去了 再见啊 城
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.45,0:05:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.96,0:05:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜酒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.35,0:05:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啦 龙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.67,0:05:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城 你的羽绒服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.05,0:05:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错吧 不久前新买的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.69,0:05:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概被火星烧了很多洞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.87,0:06:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.56,0:06:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 不拜神社了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.03,0:06:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易到这了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.15,0:06:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.52,0:06:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都没和他好好解释就把他抓来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.89,0:06:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快去快去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.55,0:06:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我下次请你吃拉面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.84,0:06:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 不用了 会胖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.37,0:06:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好贵啊 但是 就剩我们俩了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.36,0:06:34.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙 干吗啊 一个人就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.53,0:06:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 太傻了 不想待在这了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.02,0:06:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的那么认真
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.87,0:06:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是能更活泼点多好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.98,0:06:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 试着叫我“千”试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.57,0:06:50.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.08,0:06:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.15,0:06:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.83,0:06:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑着多好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.36,0:07:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管黑沼遇到什么事或者遇到熟人 翔太都会搞定的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.79,0:07:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话是没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.93,0:07:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用管他们了 你管的太宽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.66,0:07:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家也想看看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.91,0:07:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 根本不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.56,0:07:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进展的好像很顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.10,0:07:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.27,0:07:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我喝了甜酒就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在开什么玩笑 你要陪我去拜神社
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.30,0:07:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜酒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.20,0:07:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5 4 3 2 1
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.62,0:07:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新年快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.57,0:07:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你新年快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.75,0:07:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年也多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.89,0:08:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也请你多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.03,0:08:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经是新年...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 有短信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.88,0:08:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 有短信 2条
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.62,0:08:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}发信人 吉田千鹤 主题 给爽子 新（年）快（乐）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.35,0:08:24.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}发信人 矢野绫音 主题 爽子收 今年也请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.71,0:08:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小千和绫音发来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不回复吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.58,0:08:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.38,0:08:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新 年...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.60,0:08:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,短信也被抢先了啊 不过 算啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.03,0:08:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托你们的福我很开心 谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.90,0:08:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽子回短信了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.13,0:08:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你新年快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.79,0:08:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年也请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.85,0:09:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}十分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.99,0:09:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年全是“出生以来没有遇到过的”经历
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.45,0:09:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑沼 到我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.23,0:09:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想了很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.25,0:09:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了很多经历
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.85,0:09:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为遇到了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.09,0:09:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远不会忘怀的一年
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.05,0:09:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.56,0:09:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里很滑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.26,0:09:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.03,0:10:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.22,0:10:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥说他元旦回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.65,0:10:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.86,0:10:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还没记住人家的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.78,0:10:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.89,0:10:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家叫小遥吧 你认真一点啦 那可是要成为你嫂子的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会去玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.16,0:10:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙 如果你要是遇到什么伤心事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.92,0:11:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会去安慰你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.14,0:11:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那时候就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.29,0:11:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去抽签吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.40,0:11:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是大吉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.84,0:11:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.23,0:11:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有心想事成之运
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.58,0:11:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切记性急 请谨慎行事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.64,0:11:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇事请冷静的与他人商量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.70,0:11:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能办到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.03,0:11:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.24,0:12:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是小吉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.32,0:12:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说是大吉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.79,0:12:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待过头了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.93,0:12:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么说呢 我最近太贪得无厌了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.20,0:12:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑沼 你是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.73,0:12:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.61,0:12:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}恋爱运 现在的这个人是最好的 不要迷惘
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.09,0:12:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是凶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.91,0:12:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好的...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.76,0:12:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都没错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.55,0:12:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说凶反而是运气好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.46,0:12:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为很少见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.73,0:12:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 是这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.60,0:12:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的是要系在树上的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.07,0:12:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑沼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.79,0:12:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个给黑沼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.35,0:12:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风早的大吉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.20,0:13:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那该怎么说好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.51,0:13:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好像要把风早同学的运气都吸光了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.68,0:13:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系哦 就算吸光了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.62,0:13:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我运气很好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.67,0:13:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.53,0:13:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我想给你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.58,0:13:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说作为生日礼物是寒酸了点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:35.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.00,0:13:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的会有“迷惘”吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.65,0:13:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在想想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.26,0:13:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当初为什么会烦恼这是不是恋爱之情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.13,0:13:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.31,0:14:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不明白 为什么只是把风做同学当做是一种憧憬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.03,0:14:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.41,0:14:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和绫音两人独处一起过年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.98,0:14:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.08,0:14:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.48,0:14:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说好了让你在篝火那等着的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 真是抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.14,0:14:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 现在是关键时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.48,0:14:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家的笨儿子真是没药救了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.04,0:14:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.92,0:14:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走 回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.78,0:14:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.17,0:14:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么丢人 不给你压岁钱了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.21,0:14:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.23,0:14:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.35,0:14:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神啊 请务必把我和城一起度过新年的事实彻底清除掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.32,0:14:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这一个愿望 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.24,0:15:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似进展的不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.49,0:15:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也去抽根签吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.27,0:15:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 那样子看来真像普通的男女朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.39,0:15:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.62,0:15:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,废话真是多啊 不是说不要了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.42,0:15:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么嘛 不就是去喝喝酒嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.05,0:15:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋真是多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.67,0:15:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时候有彻在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.23,0:15:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能用超随便的说法搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.74,0:15:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙居然说年三十要去女朋友家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.69,0:15:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结什么婚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.83,0:15:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要看那人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.98,0:15:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 你一个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.60,0:15:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于见到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.40,0:15:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 你真是很可爱啊 经常被人这么说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.57,0:16:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,fall in love
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.65,0:16:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.75,0:16:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我邮件地址吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.28,0:16:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对戴眼镜的男生有什么看法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.23,0:16:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.57,0:16:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.79,0:16:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下辈子再一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.09,0:16:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.88,0:16:36.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么是你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.41,0:16:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太嚣张了 居然被搭讪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.19,0:16:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说刚才的白痴是你么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.49,0:16:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你要跟过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.50,0:16:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对小P孩没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.71,0:16:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真烦人 别跟过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.46,0:16:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别乱叫 我要回家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.93,0:16:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要回家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.64,0:16:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真丢人 快离我远点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.30,0:17:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登上这条坡道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.16,0:17:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是平时上学走的路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.56,0:17:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.43,0:18:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是和黑沼第一次相遇的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.63,0:18:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.27,0:18:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年会是怎么样的一年呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.06,0:18:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.94,0:18:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.15,0:18:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 能看到那个空房吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.07,0:18:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.74,0:18:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说那里也会出现哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.04,0:18:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.19,0:18:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.62,0:18:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 会出现什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.62,0:18:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 别扔下我一个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.61,0:19:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐 胡桃 许了什么愿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.67,0:19:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.95,0:19:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.19,0:19:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.83,0:19:13.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点点就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.24,0:19:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就一点点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.28,0:19:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.29,0:19:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薯片吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.74,0:19:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许不错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.05,0:19:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.90,0:19:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新年快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.34,0:19:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.74,0:19:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起过年 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.37,0:19:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.15,0:19:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说就我们这些人再去欢乐下么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.34,0:19:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你表情下流哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.04,0:19:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽子 还不回来么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.40,0:19:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.76,0:20:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来来 很甜的哦 啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.58,0:20:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很甜诶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.48,0:20:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再来一个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.82,0:20:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.96,0:20:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.33,0:20:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就下次见了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.48,0:20:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 谢谢 今天很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.39,0:20:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.24,0:20:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.72,0:21:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.13,0:21:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性急 我能克制的住么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.00,0:21:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没信心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.82,0:21:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱运
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.92,0:21:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奉献你的爱 就会幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.92,0:21:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同级生 旁边座位上的男生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.31,0:22:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.07,0:22:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然好像不仅是“朋友”
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.62,0:22:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比朋友更遥远的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.47,0:22:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比朋友更加贪得无厌的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.22,0:22:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢的人

